snippet.title: Cut the Rope: Experiments - Trailer
snippet.description:
Om Nom is back and he's hungrier than ever! Team up with the Professor to find new and crazy ways to feed Om Nom his candy. If you like Cut the Rope, you'll love Cut the Rope: Experiments.
